FBIS4-62053 "drsov092_d_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 Regional Affairs Belgorod City Administration Chief Being Replaced Belgorod City Administration Chief Being Replaced PM1105152594 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 11 May 94 First Edition p 1 PM1105152594 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Unattributed report under the "Official" rubric] [Text] By an edict of the Russian Federation president, Yuriy Ivanovich Seliverstov has been released from his post as head of administration of the city of Belgorod in Belgorod Oblast in connection with his election as chairman of Belgorod Oblast Assembly of National Representatives (Point 5 of Article 29 of the Russian Federation Labor Law Code). The Belgorod Oblast head of administration has been instructed to submit a candidacy for the post of acting head of administration of Belgorod city in Belgorod Oblast within the next seven days.
